Y           yank
YY          yank line
D           delete
DD          delete line
C           change
CC          change line
P           paste after
SHIFT-P     paste before
R           replace one character
X           delete character
SHIFT-X     delete previous character
>           indent
>>          indent line
<           unindent
<<          unindent line
J           join next line
K           go to manual entry for word
U           undo
SHIFT-U     undo changes to current line
.           repeat last change
Qx          record macro at x
Q           stop recording macro
@x          run macro at x

